{{Quote|The DL-18 for my hip, the sleeve gun for surprise, and... yes the lightsaber. Old fashioned, but useful.|[[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]]|<ref name="BtEH">''[[Star Wars: Mara Jade – By the Emperor's Hand]]''</ref>}}
[[File:SleeveGun-poly165.jpg|thumb|[[Tof Soren Hideout Pistol]], a type of sleeve gun.]]
A '''sleeve gun''' was a small, short-range [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] or [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrower]] that was concealed up a being's sleeve for surprise. Often they were mounted in special spring-loaded rigs that could thrust the gun into a waiting hand ready to fire.

